<subSubSection box="[199,1437,1821,1846]" pageId="21" pageNumber="322" type="etymology">
<paragraph blockId="21.[151,1437,151,2024]" box="[199,1437,1821,1846]" pageId="21" pageNumber="322">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,334,1821,1846]" pageId="21" pageNumber="322">Etymology.</emphasis>
the name derives from Latin and is named for its dark legs; 
<emphasis box="[1007,1072,1823,1846]" italics="true" pageId="21" pageNumber="322">perna</emphasis>
= legs + 
<emphasis box="[1176,1259,1821,1846]" italics="true" pageId="21" pageNumber="322">aquilus</emphasis>
= dark colored.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection lastPageId="23" lastPageNumber="324" pageId="21" pageNumber="322" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="21.[151,1437,151,2024]" pageId="21" pageNumber="322">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,332,1857,1882]" pageId="21" pageNumber="322">Discussion.</emphasis>
here described as a new species, but previously treated as the female of 
<taxonomicName box="[1166,1251,1858,1881]" class="Insecta" family="Tabanidae" genus="Pityocera" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="21" pageNumber="322" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="nana">
<emphasis box="[1166,1251,1858,1881]" italics="true" pageId="21" pageNumber="322">P. nana</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
in 
<bibRefCitation author="Henriques" pageId="21" pageNumber="322" refString="Henriques, A. L. &amp; Gorayeb, I. S. (1993) A colecao de Tabanidae (Insecta: Diptera) do Museu Paraense Emilio Goeldi (MPEG), Belem, Para, Brasil. Goeldiana Zoologia, 20, 1 - 23." type="journal article" year="1993">
Henriques &amp; Gorayeb (
<number box="[263,321,1893,1917]" pageId="21" pageNumber="322" value="1993.0">1993</number>
)
</bibRefCitation>
and 
<bibRefCitation author="Henriques" box="[383,583,1892,1917]" pageId="21" pageNumber="322" refString="Henriques, A. L. (1997) A colecao de Tabanidae (Insecta: Diptera) do Instituto Nacional de Pesquisas da Amazonia (INPA), Manaus, Amazonas, Brasil. Boletim do Museu Paraense Emilio Goeldi, serie Zoologia, 11 (1), 57 - 99. [1995]" type="journal article" year="1997">
Henriques (
<number box="[514,575,1893,1917]" pageId="21" pageNumber="322" value="1997.0">1997</number>
)
</bibRefCitation>
. This mistake is possibly related to the fact that a specimen from the 
<collectionCode box="[1358,1436,1893,1917]" httpUri="http://grbio.org/cool/90vz-swjg" name="Museu Paraense Emilio Goeldi" pageId="21" pageNumber="322">MPEG</collectionCode>
was identified as such by Fairchild in 
<number box="[577,636,1928,1952]" pageId="21" pageNumber="322" value="1981.0">1981</number>
. Such occurrence raises the possibility that 
<taxonomicName box="[1125,1208,1929,1952]" class="Insecta" family="Tabanidae" genus="Pityocera" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="21" pageNumber="322" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="nana">
<emphasis box="[1125,1208,1929,1952]" italics="true" pageId="21" pageNumber="322">P. nana</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
may also have been misidentified in other works (
<bibRefCitation author="Fairchild" box="[492,763,1963,1988]" pageId="21" pageNumber="322" refString="Fairchild, G. B. &amp; Leon, L. A. (1986) Lista provisional de Tabanidae (Diptera) del Ecuador. Publicaciones del Museo Ecuatoriano de Ciencias Naturales, 5, 97 - 122." type="journal article" year="1986">
Fairchild &amp; León 
<number box="[704,763,1963,1988]" pageId="21" pageNumber="322" value="1986.0">1986</number>
</bibRefCitation>
; 
<bibRefCitation author="Chainey" box="[777,1008,1963,1988]" pageId="21" pageNumber="322" refString="Chainey, J. E., Hall, M. J. R., Amayo, J. L. &amp; Bettella, P. (1994) A preliminary checklist and key to the genera and subgenera of Tabanidae (Diptera) of Bolivia with particular reference to Santa Cruz Department. Memorias do Instituto Oswaldo Cruz, 89, 321 - 345. http: // dx. doi. org / 10.1590 / s 0074 - 02761994000300007" type="journal article" year="1994">
Chainey 
<emphasis box="[880,932,1963,1988]" italics="true" pageId="21" pageNumber="322">et al</emphasis>
. 
<number box="[948,1008,1964,1988]" pageId="21" pageNumber="322" value="1994.0">1994</number>
</bibRefCitation>
; 
<bibRefCitation author="Buestan" box="[1022,1249,1963,1988]" pageId="21" pageNumber="322" refString="Buestan J. A., Navarrete, R. A. &amp; Mejia, M. T. (2007) Lista actualizada de tabanos (Diptera: Tabanidae) del Ecuador. Revista Ecuatoriana de Higiene y Medicina Tropical, 44 (1), 23 - 78." type="journal article" year="2007">
